			<p>I have it too.. but not nearly as bad, because I don&#8217;t randomly poop.</p>
<p>But lying on the floor of the bathroom wanting to rip out your stomach or die isn&#8217;t fancy pants either.</p>
<p>Anyway, I have the raccoon eyes going on.. feel your pain :)</p>
<p>really enjoyed the comic..</p>
<p>xoxox</p>
<p>Sam.</p>

