			<p>Well done &#8211; nothing to be embarrassed about&#8230;.people should be supportive and compassionate of people with Crohns, IBS, colitis and other such things.  I&#8217;m hopeful the the SC diet may be of help to folks&#8230;great job, Tom!</p>

