				<strong>Lisa T.</strong> said, on January 28th, 2011 at <a href="http://ventedspleen.com/blog/2007/10/22/24-hour-comic-everything-you-never-wanted-to-know-about-crohns-disease/comment-page-6/#comment-20488">4:22 pm</a>
